WEBVTT

00:00:00.510 --> 00:00:02.170
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

00:00:02.170 --> 00:00:03.810
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

00:00:03.810 --> 00:00:05.180
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

00:00:06.950 --> 00:00:08.350
(Episode 4)

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:22.390
- Honey, are you all right?
- Yes, I'm fine.

00:00:23.530 --> 00:00:25.830
I've safely moved your sister
into the car.

00:00:26.360 --> 00:00:27.370
Thank you.

00:00:29.270 --> 00:00:31.040
I'll go with her
to the funeral home.

00:00:31.040 --> 00:00:33.000
You go straight to our house, okay?

00:00:33.710 --> 00:00:35.840
- Be careful.
- Don't worry.

00:00:38.940 --> 00:00:40.380
We should get out of here too.

00:00:40.680 --> 00:00:41.680
Alright.

00:00:42.550 --> 00:00:43.550
Let's go.

00:00:46.080 --> 00:00:47.590
Find them now!

00:01:22.750 --> 00:01:23.820
This must've been so hard on you.

00:01:24.760 --> 00:01:25.920
I'm so sorry.

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:27.390
Not at all.

00:01:28.060 --> 00:01:30.960
A possible suspect was working
with the police.

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:32.060
It's better to be safe.

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:34.870
The baby's life could be in danger.

00:01:35.070 --> 00:01:36.730
Thank you for understanding.

00:01:39.640 --> 00:01:41.510
I feel like I've been such a burden
to you, Doctor.

00:01:42.340 --> 00:01:44.140
This must all be fate,
don't you think?

00:01:45.080 --> 00:01:46.740
So what's next for you?

00:01:47.880 --> 00:01:50.110
First, I'm going to get the baby
to a safe place,

00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:52.520
and then figure out
my sister's connection to them.

00:01:55.620 --> 00:01:56.920
Shoot.

00:01:58.160 --> 00:01:59.660
I left Kim Myung Hui's autopsy report...

00:01:59.660 --> 00:02:01.190
and the blood evidence in my office,

00:02:01.190 --> 00:02:02.260
and I forgot to bring them with me.

00:02:02.730 --> 00:02:04.300
It could be crucial evidence.

00:02:04.860 --> 00:02:05.900
Don't worry.

00:02:06.100 --> 00:02:08.170
I'll go back for them
when the coast is clear.

00:02:08.970 --> 00:02:09.970
Right.

00:02:11.340 --> 00:02:13.970
Here. They're in my desk drawer.

00:02:14.340 --> 00:02:16.070
It's key evidence
to catch the killer,

00:02:16.070 --> 00:02:17.180
so make sure you get it.

00:02:21.980 --> 00:02:22.980
Thank you.

00:02:23.150 --> 00:02:26.520
I wish I could help you more,
but I have a flight to catch.

00:02:27.590 --> 00:02:29.450
You've already helped me
more than enough.

00:02:30.460 --> 00:02:32.890
I'll never forget
what you've done for me.

00:02:33.890 --> 00:02:36.730
I hope it all gets sorted out.

00:02:41.830 --> 00:02:43.000
Drive safely.

00:03:05.690 --> 00:03:06.790
They're nowhere to be found.

00:03:09.060 --> 00:03:12.060
I searched the whole neighborhood,
but nothing.

00:03:14.530 --> 00:03:16.800
So you're just going to give up
and lie here?

00:03:17.170 --> 00:03:19.840
We have to find them
before Tae Ho's people do.

00:03:20.040 --> 00:03:22.870
We can't find them.
And neither can they.

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:28.010
No matter how I look at it,

00:03:28.380 --> 00:03:30.250
we're being played by a ghost.

00:03:30.450 --> 00:03:31.750
Enough with that stupid ghost story.

00:03:31.950 --> 00:03:32.950
A dead woman...

00:03:33.180 --> 00:03:34.650
came to the hospital to give birth,

00:03:34.720 --> 00:03:37.060
and then vanished into thin air.

00:03:37.060 --> 00:03:39.290
What else could it be but a ghost?

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:41.230
Ghost or not, I don't care.

00:03:41.230 --> 00:03:42.690
Just go and find her now.

00:03:42.790 --> 00:03:45.160
If you can't, at least stick close
to Park Tae Ho's men.

00:03:45.400 --> 00:03:48.630
If I do that,
I'll just get beaten up again.

00:03:49.200 --> 00:03:51.570
Then get beaten up, for all I care.

00:03:51.970 --> 00:03:53.740
If Tae Ho finds the baby,

00:03:54.040 --> 00:03:56.040
snatch it from him
by any means necessary.

00:03:56.040 --> 00:03:59.440
Wait, I was so panicked earlier
that I didn't even think of this,

00:04:00.210 --> 00:04:02.750
but what are you planning to do
once we snatch the baby?

00:04:03.050 --> 00:04:06.620
If we make one wrong move,
Tae Ho will kill us.

00:04:06.680 --> 00:04:08.990
I'm doing this so I can stay alive.

00:04:09.420 --> 00:04:11.960
Would he let us off
once he finds the baby?

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:14.030
Will he acknowledge my child...

00:04:14.030 --> 00:04:16.290
once he finds his precious son?

00:04:17.360 --> 00:04:20.230
To protect ourselves and my child
from Tae Ho,

00:04:20.600 --> 00:04:23.030
our only option is
to take the baby hostage.

00:04:24.040 --> 00:04:25.300
A hostage?

00:04:26.200 --> 00:04:28.140
We'll hide the baby
out of his reach.

00:04:28.610 --> 00:04:30.580
If we take the baby hostage,

00:04:30.980 --> 00:04:34.110
we'll have leverage over him.

00:04:34.410 --> 00:04:37.520
As if that kind of blackmail
would work on someone like him.

00:04:39.950 --> 00:04:40.990
So?

00:04:41.550 --> 00:04:44.390
Am I supposed to just let
that wretch's child have it all?

00:04:44.660 --> 00:04:47.660
My child's future will be ruined,
so we have to try something,

00:04:47.660 --> 00:04:49.630
even if it's threats
or a desperate fight.

00:04:49.660 --> 00:04:51.630
So, get it together, darn it!

00:04:54.430 --> 00:04:56.230
Go find something right now,

00:04:56.230 --> 00:04:58.200
whether it's the darn baby
or a plan!

00:05:00.410 --> 00:05:02.570
(Baek OB-GYN)

00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:23.460
Kim Myung Hui had a baby?

00:05:28.700 --> 00:05:30.400
You're sure it's my child?

00:05:31.400 --> 00:05:32.900
Yes, I'm certain.

00:05:35.540 --> 00:05:36.970
Then why are you
just standing around?

00:05:38.310 --> 00:05:42.080
- Sorry?
- Bring me the doctor right now.

00:05:42.910 --> 00:05:45.780
He's the only person who knows
about Kim Myung Hui and the child.

00:05:48.220 --> 00:05:49.420
Sir, with all due respect,

00:05:49.420 --> 00:05:50.960
I thought this was just
a simple errand...

00:05:50.960 --> 00:05:53.060
when the chief assigned me here.

00:05:53.890 --> 00:05:55.790
But this has gotten way out of hand.

00:05:56.760 --> 00:05:59.030
Other cases need my attention,

00:05:59.030 --> 00:06:00.700
so I can't get stuck on this one.

00:06:04.600 --> 00:06:05.900
Mr. Park!

00:06:12.540 --> 00:06:14.280
Chief, it's me.

00:06:16.180 --> 00:06:19.180
It's about that Detective Yun
you sent over.

00:06:21.490 --> 00:06:23.760
He seems to be quite a capable man.

00:06:25.090 --> 00:06:27.260
I'd like to keep him on
a bit longer.

00:06:27.460 --> 00:06:28.830
Would that be all right?

00:06:31.500 --> 00:06:35.870
Thank you. I'll make sure
to show my appreciation.

00:06:40.570 --> 00:06:42.170
That clears things up, doesn't it?

00:06:50.920 --> 00:06:52.280
This only got out of hand...

00:06:52.280 --> 00:06:55.750
because you were pathetic enough
to lose my son.

00:06:57.120 --> 00:06:59.260
If you don't take responsibility
and fix this,

00:07:00.490 --> 00:07:03.360
or if you think
you can just walk away,

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:07.970
you'll pay a heavy price...

00:07:08.830 --> 00:07:10.470
for underestimating me...

00:07:11.640 --> 00:07:13.300
for a very long time.

00:07:16.410 --> 00:07:17.410
Understood.

00:07:26.150 --> 00:07:27.220
I was just...

00:07:28.020 --> 00:07:29.990
checking on the situation...

00:07:29.990 --> 00:07:31.960
and ran into the detective.

00:07:40.200 --> 00:07:41.300
Stay put.

00:07:42.130 --> 00:07:44.870
Don't do a thing.
Just stay out of it.

00:07:48.970 --> 00:07:52.110
This is your last chance
to save that pathetic life of yours.

00:08:02.850 --> 00:08:04.890
(Baek OB-GYN)

00:08:13.730 --> 00:08:16.730
Why did a doctor here
take Kim Myung Hui?

00:08:17.770 --> 00:08:18.770
Unless...

00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:21.110
Could someone else be involved?

00:08:22.110 --> 00:08:23.610
But who?

00:08:24.380 --> 00:08:25.510
And why?

00:08:34.350 --> 00:08:36.620
These people even have the police
in their pocket.

00:08:37.220 --> 00:08:38.860
I need to be more careful.

00:08:39.720 --> 00:08:42.390
What on earth was their connection
to Myung Hui?

00:08:44.330 --> 00:08:46.360
There, there.

00:08:46.900 --> 00:08:48.170
It's okay.

00:08:55.540 --> 00:08:57.210
You have her eyes.

00:08:58.710 --> 00:09:00.410
You look just like your mom.

00:09:02.980 --> 00:09:03.980
That's right.

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:06.250
I look like her too, don't I?

00:09:07.050 --> 00:09:09.020
Don't I have your mom's face?

00:09:10.790 --> 00:09:13.820
You're just a newborn,
so everything's a blur,

00:09:14.090 --> 00:09:16.130
but you can see it with your heart,
can't you?

00:09:24.700 --> 00:09:25.800
Even so,

00:09:27.240 --> 00:09:29.210
don't dwell
on your mom's last moments...

00:09:29.740 --> 00:09:31.240
for too long.

00:09:33.380 --> 00:09:35.380
And don't look too closely
at the people...

00:09:36.180 --> 00:09:37.680
who are trying to kill you.

00:09:40.550 --> 00:09:42.750
All the sad and ugly things
in the world?

00:09:44.190 --> 00:09:46.160
It's better to just
let them be a blur.

00:09:50.430 --> 00:09:52.360
Dan Hui!

00:09:52.500 --> 00:09:53.630
Dan Hui!

00:10:04.510 --> 00:10:06.310
I'll do my very best for you.

00:10:07.750 --> 00:10:09.450
I'll work hard to make sure...

00:10:09.450 --> 00:10:11.950
the world you see is a happy one.

00:10:13.750 --> 00:10:15.290
So your mom...

00:10:15.850 --> 00:10:17.560
can finally find some peace.

00:10:28.270 --> 00:10:31.400
All right, here is
the Jung Woo Jin special.

00:10:32.200 --> 00:10:33.300
Go on, dig in.

00:10:33.900 --> 00:10:36.570
Even the head
of the cooking school...

00:10:36.570 --> 00:10:37.840
said this stew was amazing.

00:10:43.480 --> 00:10:45.680
I know it feels weird...

00:10:45.880 --> 00:10:48.250
to be having a proper meal
at a time like this.

00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:50.820
Even my sister,
who eats five meals a day,

00:10:51.120 --> 00:10:54.260
could barely eat one
when our parents passed away.

00:10:54.530 --> 00:10:56.730
But it's times like this...

00:11:02.030 --> 00:11:03.200
Look at you dig in.

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:07.740
The baby was so heavy.

00:11:09.870 --> 00:11:10.910
What?

00:11:12.180 --> 00:11:14.150
But he's so tiny.

00:11:18.680 --> 00:11:19.850
Carrying him felt heavier,

00:11:20.320 --> 00:11:23.120
knowing his life was in my hands.

00:11:26.390 --> 00:11:28.230
I have to protect him,

00:11:28.890 --> 00:11:31.060
so I can't afford to collapse
from exhaustion.

00:11:32.630 --> 00:11:33.960
For my sister's sake,

00:11:35.100 --> 00:11:36.500
I have to protect her baby.

00:11:46.840 --> 00:11:47.950
Have some meat.

00:11:48.210 --> 00:11:49.480
That'll give you strength.

00:11:59.690 --> 00:12:02.830
So what happens next?

00:12:03.590 --> 00:12:05.430
There's Myung Hui's funeral
to think about.

00:12:05.960 --> 00:12:09.030
Shouldn't we find the father
and contact him first?

00:12:09.900 --> 00:12:12.200
Let's postpone the funeral
for a few days.

00:12:14.110 --> 00:12:16.310
First, I need to find out...

00:12:16.610 --> 00:12:18.480
who killed Myung Hui.

00:12:19.510 --> 00:12:22.410
If the baby's father is involved,

00:12:22.610 --> 00:12:23.980
things could get dangerous.

00:12:25.180 --> 00:12:27.920
Do you think we can find them
in just a few days?

00:12:28.290 --> 00:12:30.990
Going to the police doesn't seem
like an option right now.

00:12:31.790 --> 00:12:35.490
First, I'll go back to the neighborhood
where Myung Hui lived.

00:12:36.230 --> 00:12:38.900
Maybe someone there knows
who the baby's father is...

00:12:38.960 --> 00:12:40.630
and who killed her.

00:12:41.230 --> 00:12:45.100
And we also need to get the evidence
from the hospital.

00:12:46.000 --> 00:12:47.510
I'll handle the hospital.

00:12:47.740 --> 00:12:49.710
It's too dangerous for you to go.

00:12:50.210 --> 00:12:53.440
Then I'll go check out
the neighborhood.

00:12:53.710 --> 00:12:56.050
I'll use my experience
charming moms at my cooking class...

00:12:56.510 --> 00:12:57.920
to win over the ladies there.

00:12:58.680 --> 00:12:59.750
Good.

00:13:00.520 --> 00:13:02.020
Make yourself useful for a change.

00:13:02.120 --> 00:13:04.490
You're one to talk. Hey, hold on.

00:13:05.620 --> 00:13:08.390
- Let go, will you?
- Pull your weight for once.

00:13:08.460 --> 00:13:10.130
You always shove me around.

00:13:10.190 --> 00:13:12.300
- Seriously, let go!
- What are you doing sitting around?

00:13:12.360 --> 00:13:14.030
I mean it. Let go of me.

00:13:14.130 --> 00:13:16.830
Keep it down. You'll wake the baby.

00:13:17.130 --> 00:13:18.140
Be quiet.

00:13:21.910 --> 00:13:25.680
I'll go to the funeral home first,
then head to the hospital.

00:13:26.440 --> 00:13:27.480
Watch your back.

00:13:28.280 --> 00:13:30.810
Don't worry about me
and just get some rest.

00:13:31.450 --> 00:13:33.880
And you. Don't mess things up
in that neighborhood.

00:13:33.980 --> 00:13:36.090
You just worry about yourself.

00:13:37.350 --> 00:13:38.920
But be careful.

00:13:41.090 --> 00:13:42.190
I'll see you later.

00:13:47.570 --> 00:13:48.570
Woo Jin.

00:13:49.570 --> 00:13:50.830
Can you watch the baby for me?

00:13:52.870 --> 00:13:55.510
I'll check out her old neighborhood.

00:13:56.010 --> 00:13:58.580
Why? I can do a good job too.

00:13:58.840 --> 00:14:00.710
It's not that I don't trust you.

00:14:00.810 --> 00:14:02.550
I just need to see it for myself.

00:14:03.410 --> 00:14:06.780
The neighborhood she lived in
and her house.

00:14:08.050 --> 00:14:09.990
I want to go back
and take it all in.

00:14:10.250 --> 00:14:12.260
Then let's go together.

00:14:12.690 --> 00:14:14.020
Who'll watch the baby?

00:14:17.230 --> 00:14:20.200
I'll be careful. Don't worry.

00:14:23.730 --> 00:14:25.170
Dan Hui, wait a second.

00:14:29.910 --> 00:14:32.440
Here. Use this if you're in danger.

00:14:34.450 --> 00:14:36.050
And call me if anything happens.

00:14:37.750 --> 00:14:39.250
Okay, thanks.

00:14:48.660 --> 00:14:49.660
Be careful.

00:14:54.600 --> 00:14:55.600
See that?

00:14:56.400 --> 00:14:57.900
Your aunt is so brave.

00:14:59.000 --> 00:15:01.170
She makes people worry sick,

00:15:02.140 --> 00:15:03.410
but she's also really cool.

00:15:05.210 --> 00:15:06.340
When you get older,

00:15:06.780 --> 00:15:08.910
you'd better be good to your aunt,
you hear me?

00:15:16.990 --> 00:15:18.120
Jin Ju.

00:15:18.890 --> 00:15:21.530
Your name is Jin Ju. Baek Jin Ju.

00:15:24.300 --> 00:15:26.360
Looks like Jin Ju likes her name.

00:15:26.660 --> 00:15:28.430
She's flashing me a big smile.

00:15:30.200 --> 00:15:31.670
I knew she would.

00:15:32.440 --> 00:15:33.670
I dreamed of a giant pearl,

00:15:33.670 --> 00:15:36.510
white as the moon,
before she was born.

00:15:41.180 --> 00:15:43.150
Don't worry too much.

00:15:43.450 --> 00:15:45.320
It won't be that long.

00:15:46.280 --> 00:15:48.020
As soon as
Jin Ju's passport is ready,

00:15:48.450 --> 00:15:49.790
we'll join you right away.

00:15:50.020 --> 00:15:52.320
I'm sorry I can't stick around.

00:15:52.590 --> 00:15:55.630
Well, it is what it is.

00:15:56.090 --> 00:16:01.030
Still, I get to recover
in a nice place like this.

00:16:02.470 --> 00:16:03.770
I hope our Jin Ju...

00:16:04.400 --> 00:16:06.540
grows up to be just like you.

00:16:06.740 --> 00:16:09.540
Stop. She should take after you.

00:16:10.270 --> 00:16:12.840
I'm going to raise her
to be smart...

00:16:12.910 --> 00:16:15.280
and warmhearted, just like you.

00:16:21.450 --> 00:16:23.250
Do you think Kim Dan Hui
will be all right?

00:16:23.950 --> 00:16:26.360
I can't help but worry...

00:16:26.960 --> 00:16:28.530
since she's the one
who delivered Jin Ju.

00:16:29.390 --> 00:16:32.500
It bothers me too
that I couldn't do more to help her.

00:16:33.560 --> 00:16:36.270
I really hope she manages
to find the evidence in my office.

00:16:47.580 --> 00:16:49.080
Let's just go home.

00:16:49.250 --> 00:16:52.120
Tae Ho told us to stay put.

00:16:52.720 --> 00:16:54.180
How can I trust him?

00:16:54.690 --> 00:16:57.420
We have to find the baby
before he does and hide him.

00:16:57.720 --> 00:16:59.190
Jung Ran, please!

00:17:02.160 --> 00:17:04.430
Tae Ho was right about one thing.
That doctor...

00:17:06.200 --> 00:17:07.770
is the only witness.

00:17:09.330 --> 00:17:10.570
Find anything you can on him.

00:17:11.030 --> 00:17:13.670
We need to get to that doctor first.

00:17:14.710 --> 00:17:16.410
One minute you don't trust him,

00:17:16.410 --> 00:17:18.080
the next you think he is right.

00:17:18.080 --> 00:17:19.340
Park Tae Ho this, Park Tae Ho that.

00:17:19.340 --> 00:17:22.210
Get him out of your life already!

00:17:24.210 --> 00:17:25.420
This is it.

00:17:30.220 --> 00:17:32.360
Gosh, are you okay?

00:17:32.420 --> 00:17:35.290
Wait. Get off me!

00:17:43.700 --> 00:17:44.700
What's wrong?

00:17:45.970 --> 00:17:47.040
Is it your stomach?

00:17:47.440 --> 00:17:48.510
See?

00:17:48.610 --> 00:17:50.840
This is what happens when
you run around screaming all day.

00:17:50.910 --> 00:17:53.010
Of course the baby is exhausted!

00:17:53.340 --> 00:17:55.150
Shut it, will you?

00:17:55.150 --> 00:17:57.680
Take me to a doctor, now!

00:17:58.220 --> 00:18:01.150
- Let's get you up. Careful.
- Be gentle.

00:18:04.090 --> 00:18:06.020
We're almost there.

00:18:11.090 --> 00:18:12.100
- Careful.
- Slowly.

00:18:17.770 --> 00:18:20.040
Gosh, my stomach...

00:18:22.670 --> 00:18:25.340
My stomach... Hurry.

00:18:26.180 --> 00:18:27.680
Hang in there.

00:18:29.980 --> 00:18:33.520
(Baek OB-GYN)

00:18:53.940 --> 00:18:55.540
Wait, was it them?

00:18:57.140 --> 00:18:59.140
How will Myung Hui get justice now?

00:18:59.340 --> 00:19:01.110
Oh, no. Our poor Dan Hui!

00:19:03.250 --> 00:19:04.920
How on earth did they know...

00:19:05.780 --> 00:19:07.150
the evidence was still here?

00:19:41.420 --> 00:19:44.590
The OB-GYN left for the US.

00:19:47.160 --> 00:19:48.160
The US?

00:19:48.330 --> 00:19:50.290
Apparently, he went there to study.

00:19:50.560 --> 00:19:53.160
I guess that's why
he closed the clinic.

00:19:56.700 --> 00:19:59.770
So what did you find out
about Kim Myung Hui?

00:20:01.310 --> 00:20:03.140
As I reported last time,

00:20:03.140 --> 00:20:04.780
besides her regular hospital visits,

00:20:04.840 --> 00:20:06.410
there was nothing
out of the ordinary.

00:20:06.540 --> 00:20:09.050
Why don't you have a reason
for the hospital visits yet?

00:20:10.210 --> 00:20:11.320
About that...

00:20:12.320 --> 00:20:14.380
The hospital director...

00:20:14.450 --> 00:20:17.220
is demanding a formal warrant,

00:20:18.520 --> 00:20:20.190
which is making it hard
to find anything.

00:20:28.270 --> 00:20:30.200
Start the investigation
from scratch.

00:20:31.300 --> 00:20:34.470
I want to know exactly why
Kim Myung Hui was at that hospital.

00:20:34.910 --> 00:20:36.770
Check the orphanage
she grew up in...

00:20:36.770 --> 00:20:39.240
and every place she's ever worked!

00:20:42.750 --> 00:20:45.380
Find anyone who was close enough
to Kim Myung Hui...

00:20:46.350 --> 00:20:48.390
to help her and the baby disappear.

00:20:57.360 --> 00:20:58.360
Yes, sir.

00:21:43.140 --> 00:21:45.280
I knew it.
The police are on his payroll.

00:21:53.180 --> 00:21:55.150
Were those people
living in this house?

00:21:56.450 --> 00:21:58.760
Isn't the baby's father
supposed to live here?

00:22:02.530 --> 00:22:04.760
The level of incompetence...

00:22:21.510 --> 00:22:23.950
I was at the blue-roofed house,
down the hill.

00:22:24.720 --> 00:22:27.850
The woman who lives there is alone,
so I helped with her sick grandson.

00:22:44.870 --> 00:22:45.940
Unbelievable.

00:22:50.770 --> 00:22:52.010
How can I help you?

00:22:53.910 --> 00:22:55.010
You know Kim Myung Hui,

00:22:56.610 --> 00:22:57.610
right?

00:22:58.620 --> 00:22:59.880
Kim Myung Hui?

00:23:00.350 --> 00:23:02.220
You mean the young woman
from the villa?

00:23:02.790 --> 00:23:04.520
I'm the owner of that house.

00:23:04.960 --> 00:23:06.990
Then you must be that rotten jerk...

00:23:11.600 --> 00:23:13.400
Where is Kim Myung Hui right now?

00:23:14.400 --> 00:23:15.470
What?

00:23:16.200 --> 00:23:18.200
Why are you asking me?

00:23:18.370 --> 00:23:22.570
If you're calling me a rotten jerk,
you must know our situation.

00:23:23.710 --> 00:23:25.310
And your reaction tells me...

00:23:25.710 --> 00:23:27.880
you already knew
that Kim Myung Hui...

00:23:28.380 --> 00:23:29.380
had...

00:23:30.380 --> 00:23:31.750
disappeared.

00:23:32.050 --> 00:23:33.080
I...

00:23:34.050 --> 00:23:36.420
Well, that's...

00:23:36.420 --> 00:23:37.690
Kim Myung Hui.

00:23:38.220 --> 00:23:39.320
No, my son.

00:23:40.360 --> 00:23:42.330
Who hid him and where?

00:23:43.760 --> 00:23:45.760
How would I know that?

00:23:46.500 --> 00:23:48.060
I don't know anything.

00:23:52.170 --> 00:23:53.400
Tell me the truth.

00:23:53.500 --> 00:23:56.210
Where is my son?

00:23:56.570 --> 00:23:58.510
Let go!

00:23:58.810 --> 00:24:01.850
Leave my grandma alone!

00:24:02.480 --> 00:24:04.350
Sweetie, Grandma's fine.

00:24:04.350 --> 00:24:06.380
Go on inside now.

00:24:06.420 --> 00:24:08.820
Grandma, you're not okay.

00:24:08.820 --> 00:24:11.250
He's a bad man!

00:24:11.320 --> 00:24:14.190
- Sweetie.
- Enough!

00:24:14.620 --> 00:24:16.930
Let's not waste our energy
and end this peacefully.

00:24:17.390 --> 00:24:19.960
Your grandson must mean more to you
than Kim Myung Hui.

00:24:20.500 --> 00:24:23.200
For your grandson's sake,
tell me the truth.

00:24:23.900 --> 00:24:27.000
Where are Kim Myung Hui and my son?

00:24:35.950 --> 00:24:38.220
- What's he doing?
- What's on earth?

00:24:38.880 --> 00:24:40.380
- What's this?
- What is he doing?

00:24:41.820 --> 00:24:43.650
- Grandma!
- What's with him?

00:24:43.720 --> 00:24:47.190
- What's your problem?
- Next time, I'll bring the police.

00:24:47.520 --> 00:24:49.990
Then maybe things
you can't seem to remember...

00:24:51.630 --> 00:24:52.960
will come back to you.

00:24:53.800 --> 00:24:55.700
Right? Well, then.

00:24:57.870 --> 00:24:59.700
- That poor old lady.
- What's his problem?

00:25:03.210 --> 00:25:04.510
- What was that?
- Goodness.

00:25:04.770 --> 00:25:05.880
Goodness me.

00:25:07.040 --> 00:25:08.040
Are you all right?

00:25:08.480 --> 00:25:11.210
My goodness,
what on earth was that about?

00:25:11.310 --> 00:25:13.080
What did he want with her?

00:25:17.090 --> 00:25:18.090
Are you hurt?

00:25:18.220 --> 00:25:19.560
Are you all right?

00:25:28.630 --> 00:25:29.870
What happened?

00:25:46.380 --> 00:25:47.550
What's going on?

00:25:48.590 --> 00:25:50.120
You left,
saying you were running away,

00:25:50.990 --> 00:25:52.490
so why on earth did you come back?

00:25:55.590 --> 00:25:56.660
What about the baby?

00:25:56.930 --> 00:25:59.260
Was it a smooth delivery?

00:26:00.330 --> 00:26:02.900
I knew it.
You know my sister, don't you?

00:26:07.940 --> 00:26:08.940
Your sister?

00:26:11.610 --> 00:26:13.180
You're not the young woman
from the villa?

00:26:14.240 --> 00:26:16.410
I'm her twin sister.

00:26:18.320 --> 00:26:20.080
You're twins?

00:26:20.520 --> 00:26:23.190
But what was it you just said?

00:26:23.850 --> 00:26:26.090
My sister was running away? Why?

00:26:26.620 --> 00:26:27.620
What?

00:26:28.730 --> 00:26:30.390
Why are you asking me that?

00:26:31.900 --> 00:26:34.230
You can just ask her yourself.

00:26:39.770 --> 00:26:41.100
I can't.

00:26:42.010 --> 00:26:43.840
There's so much I want to ask her,

00:26:46.140 --> 00:26:47.980
but she's somewhere far away.

00:26:49.780 --> 00:26:50.810
She died unexpectedly,

00:26:51.550 --> 00:26:53.580
leaving me and her child behind.

00:27:00.890 --> 00:27:04.230
Are you saying
something bad happened to her?

00:27:06.700 --> 00:27:08.900
Please tell me
what was going on with my sister.

00:27:09.500 --> 00:27:11.670
I have to know
why my sister was killed.

00:27:12.670 --> 00:27:13.800
Please, ma'am. I need your help.

00:27:30.350 --> 00:27:31.820
She left me this.

00:27:41.900 --> 00:27:44.500
Your sister left this for me.

00:27:47.470 --> 00:27:50.210
(From Myung Hui)

00:27:50.410 --> 00:27:51.410
Ma'am,

00:27:52.610 --> 00:27:55.680
I'm sorry I left without a goodbye.

00:27:58.280 --> 00:27:59.450
It pains me to do this,

00:28:00.520 --> 00:28:02.790
but I have to get away from him.

00:28:04.320 --> 00:28:07.060
I can't let my child
live in this nightmare.

00:28:10.630 --> 00:28:12.600
Your sister was manipulated...

00:28:13.800 --> 00:28:17.370
by the owners of Adele,
who own the villa.

00:28:19.570 --> 00:28:22.710
She really thought
the villa owner...

00:28:23.540 --> 00:28:24.940
was a widower,

00:28:28.980 --> 00:28:32.820
but he lied to her
and even got her pregnant.

00:28:37.520 --> 00:28:38.690
This baby?

00:28:39.360 --> 00:28:40.990
I met someone I love,

00:28:42.130 --> 00:28:43.860
and I'm having his child.

00:28:44.230 --> 00:28:46.130
I didn't want him
to get the wrong idea.

00:28:46.530 --> 00:28:47.660
That I was only with him
because you're sick...

00:28:49.100 --> 00:28:51.940
and I needed the money
for your surgery.

00:28:53.170 --> 00:28:55.970
I didn't want us
to be like that because...

00:28:59.110 --> 00:29:00.480
what I felt for him was real.

00:29:03.880 --> 00:29:06.280
But his wife...

00:29:07.080 --> 00:29:09.120
kept tormenting your poor sister.

00:29:09.690 --> 00:29:11.350
She was so vicious...

00:29:12.590 --> 00:29:15.630
that the stress nearly caused her
to lose the baby.

00:29:18.090 --> 00:29:20.960
On top of that, I heard a rumor...

00:29:22.330 --> 00:29:25.670
that his wife was pregnant too.

00:29:27.270 --> 00:29:30.710
I was afraid of what else
that woman might do,

00:29:31.640 --> 00:29:33.710
so I told your sister
to leave immediately.

00:29:35.450 --> 00:29:36.780
She said she couldn't,
not right away.

00:29:38.480 --> 00:29:40.380
That there was someone
she had to protect.

00:29:46.190 --> 00:29:48.490
And by then, it was too late.

00:29:49.990 --> 00:29:52.700
Of all the men in the world,
why did she fall for him?

00:29:55.200 --> 00:29:56.270
Myung Hui...

00:30:09.910 --> 00:30:11.150
It's because of me.

00:30:12.950 --> 00:30:14.320
It's all my fault.

00:30:15.120 --> 00:30:19.090
If she hadn't tried to save me,
she wouldn't have met him.

00:30:23.990 --> 00:30:25.500
I killed my sister.

00:30:26.900 --> 00:30:30.670
Trying to save me cost her her life.

00:30:38.680 --> 00:30:39.680
I'm so sorry.

00:30:40.810 --> 00:30:42.610
I'm sorry for killing you,

00:30:45.250 --> 00:30:48.150
and I'm sorry I'm still alive.

00:30:52.620 --> 00:30:54.520
Myung Hui.

00:30:55.590 --> 00:31:00.300
Myung Hui...

00:31:04.570 --> 00:31:07.340
Myung Hui...

00:31:40.470 --> 00:31:43.310
(Pearl in Red)

00:31:44.840 --> 00:31:47.110
Dan Hui is usually tough,
so for her to be crying like this...

00:31:47.910 --> 00:31:49.010
I have a bad feeling about this.

00:31:49.510 --> 00:31:51.750
Did she just vanish into thin air?

00:31:51.810 --> 00:31:53.020
She's obviously dead,

00:31:53.020 --> 00:31:55.420
so why is there
no funeral record for her?

00:31:55.520 --> 00:31:56.550
What is this?

00:31:56.550 --> 00:31:58.620
I die so that Myung Hui can live.

00:31:58.890 --> 00:31:59.990
From this moment on,

00:31:59.990 --> 00:32:01.090
I'll become Kim Myung Hui...

00:32:01.420 --> 00:32:02.830
and live out her life.

00:32:04.630 --> 00:32:07.160
A ghost! It's a ghost!

00:32:07.530 --> 00:32:09.230
No way, this is impossible.

00:32:09.370 --> 00:32:11.970
Are you Mr. Park Tae Ho,
the president of Adele?

00:32:12.270 --> 00:32:14.940
Please, help me.
I don't remember anything.

00:32:16.770 --> 00:32:18.810
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)